 2015}} || 10 || One Israeli soldier was killed when a Palestinian en route to carry out an attack in Israel was discovered and detonated himself at a checkpoint. A second intended suicide bomber was also killed in the blast as well as the driver and a third passenger.{{dubious|'THE" driver means, the bomber's driver & co-conspirator? Was the "passenger" a victim or an accomplice?|date=January 2015}} Three soldiers and seven Palestinians were also wounded. |}
